Author: gstant1
Title: [ANN][ICO][OIO] ONLINE - Together we can change the internet 🔴|🔴
Body: Just wondering, I like the concept of OIO and what it hopes to achieve but there are some anomaly's that I see with this project.  Maybe a non-staff high ranked member here can give their input an possible reasons for the below?  If some of you could it would be very much appreciated.    Here is what I find strange (I am not making any accusations just pointing out some things that I have observed)  Their ICO was apparently sold out, over $50 Million USD, and their ERC20 contract has over 15 thousand addresses https://etherscan.io/token/0xa3efef1a1e3d1ad72b9d0f4253e7c9c084c2c08b  And they are following their road-map and afaik have not missed any deadlines.  Most ICO ratings websites gave them 4+ stars, so again very good.  So reading the above you would think, all good this is a project with legs and with some potential.  But.....  1.  No one seems to talk about the project online? 2.  Their Telegram has 23 thousand members but there is NEVER any conversation about the project, and nothing close to any in-depth conversations, just the odd comment here or there? 3.  They have 38 thousand followers on Twitter but no one talks or has conversations there either?  4.  On their Facebook page there are posts that receive 2 or 3 thousand likes but no one comments?  And most of the likes are seemingly from India.  (TBH it actually looks like they have paid a click farm for the Facebook likes)   So with that said, can some please explain why this would be?  Does anyone else notice the same? Is anyone posting in this thread actually invested in OIO?  Thank you.

Author: Online.io
Title: [ANN][ICO][OIO] ONLINE - Together we can change the internet 🔴|🔴
Body: Hello Everyone,  If anyone has any questions about the project or wants to hear the latest news i suggest you join our Telegram group where we post information. We are currently working very hard on the public blockchain along with the Mobile solution for the application which will include also a Residential VPN which will remove any censorship from any country in the world, even from China, Russia, etc. When we will release the VPN it will be connected to over 30M residential IPs and offer IPs from any country and city in the world. Regarding the Exchange, until we are not ready with the full solution we are not interested in listing the token. We are very confident that once we release the solution it will be used by Millions of people and demand for the token will be very big. We prefer doing the solution first then focus on exchanges. Our Extensions for Browsers has already over 20,000 active users and it's growing daily natural without any paid marketing. Once we have the full solution we will also start our global marketing campaign which we expect to bring at least 1M users in the first month.  Best regards

Body: The team should have already listed OIO on top exchanges. ICO ended at the end of July but it's a pity they raised $50m but have not even listed the token on a good exchange which could have prevented it from dumping and low rates. I get it it that the product should be primed concern but since they are planning on releasing the Alpha version of the OIO Blockchain in the second quarter of this year, I think the team should not wait till then to list OIO on a good exchange. They must target at least 1 top exchange before the release of the blockchain. Low volume exchanges are killing the potential of OIO token. As of writing this I see on coinmarketcap that OIO's last 24 hour volume is a mere $277! There's no doubt that once the product is fully ready to attract more users, it will create the natural demand for the token but being listed on a top exchange would boost investors confidence.

Author: thh2899
Title: [ANN][ICO][OIO] ONLINE - Together we can change the internet 🔴|🔴
Body: Users will be able to rate a website from 1 to 5 stars, 5 stars representing the highest quality websites, 1 star representing the lowest quality websites. The number of stars will initially be converted to Trust Rating simply by dividing them by 5 (i.e. 5 stars will represent a trust rating of 1, 2.5 stars will represent a trust rating of 0.5, 1 star will represent a trust rating of 0.2). By default, websites with no ratings will have a Trust Rating of 0.5 (equivalent of 2.5 stars). In the future, the Trust Rating formula will probably evolve to include many more factors.

Author: MrSlave
Title: [ANN][ICO][OIO] ONLINE - Together we can change the internet 🔴|🔴
Body: Some info about PoET from their whitepaper   Proof-of-elapsed time (PoET) - (Reference #4) is a relatively new concept. Coins are distributed based on the proof that the user was doing some specific action for a rather long period of real time. Proof of time algorithm was invented by Intel and it is mainly associated with their hardware platform that provides very fast consensus model. It generates random numbers (wait time) on miner’s nodes and then chooses the node with the lowest number. So, it works like a lottery but with more complex algorithm designed to provide more optimizations. Intel promises that this algorithm cannot be broken by external actions and provides honest consensus model. This makes PoET perfect for private Blockchain when you need performant distributed storage and don’t want to force your hardware to make complex computations. The only minus is the restriction on Intel’s platform (Sawtooth Lake).

Author: MaZeeCM
Title: [ANN][ICO][OIO] ONLINE - Together we can change the internet 🔴|🔴
Body: The basis of rewards for website operators will be the Proof-of-Online which is a number that quantifies how many minutes users spend on each website.  Websites will have a script embedded on them (for example http://online.io/script.js?site=site_id)  The webserver on http://online.io will be a Node.js cluster hosted behind Cloudflare.  The combination of Cloudflare's protection and our own custom implemented solution in the cluster will count real people online (multiple sessions from the same user at the same time will count as one).  The webserver will store each website's stats. Every week each website's visits will be converted to ICE tokens after a period of 7 days (visits for 1-7 of the month will be paid on the 14th, etc.).

Title: [ANN][ICO][OIO] ONLINE - Together we can change the internet 🔴|🔴
Body: Nice question! Let me explain why own tokens are necessary here: Online Ethereum token (OIO). OIO Tokens are the key element in the ecosystem. The web operators will be required to stake OIO Tokens in order to use our technology and mine ICE tokens. (through Proof-of-Stake and Proof-of-Online algorithms).  ICE Ethereum token (ICE). The purpose of the ICE coin is to be used for micropayments and daily use.  Trust token (TST). Exists only within the private Blockchain. It is used for stimulating users to rank websites and for ranking gamification.  All of them has different significance  More info: https://t.me/OnlineIO

Author: setpass
Title: [ANN][ICO][OIO] ONLINE - Together we can change the internet 🔴|🔴
Body: Our ultimate goal is to reinvent the World Wide Web experience by placing people’s privacy as our top priority, thus offering a more secure, non-trackable, without malware and ad free Internet. Government agencies and big Internet companies that shall remain unnamed thrive on tracking your every move! Only together we can put a STOP to this! Nowadays websites are full of ads that try to sell you something they think you need by creating an unfriendly and irritating browsing experience. Also, lots of them have hidden malware, scammy ads or mining scripts. Online.io platform aims at making a groundbreaking change of the Internet, by revolutionizing the browsing experience and making it faster, non-trackable, without malware and ad free. Website operators gain a significant amount of revenues from ads, which can be changed by implementing our solution based on the highly scalable, transparent and fully accountable Blockchain technology, which will ensure they get fair remuneration based on the number of visitors, time spent on their pages and the interaction with the site, creating a more suitable environment for quality, as opposed to spammy cash driven webpages

Author: MaZeeCM
Title: [ANN][ICO][OIO] ONLINE - Together we can change the internet 🔴|🔴
Body: 3 tokens - Online Ethereum token (OIO). OIO Tokens are the key element in the ecosystem. The web operators will be required to stake OIO Tokens in order to use our technology and mine ICE tokens. (through Proof-of-Stake and Proof-of-Online algorithms).  ICE Ethereum token (ICE). The purpose of the ICE coin is to be used for micropayments and daily use.  Trust token (TST). Exists only within the private Blockchain. It is used for stimulating users to rank websites and for ranking gamification.  All of them has different significance and they can be traded 😊 You can only mine ICE tokens out of these three

Title: [ANN][ICO][OIO] ONLINE - Together we can change the internet 🔴|🔴
Body: Website operators may consider that by using the Online.io solution, their revenues might be downsized since they are no longer monetizing on the ads posted, but in fact the Online.io solution will unlock an untamed potential of revenue stream. The website owners will have financial benefits even without embedding advertisements, by capitalizing on the time spent by the visitors on their webpages. Since the visitors will be able to rate the websites based on their experience, the ad free, secure, private webpages will definitely enjoy a higher ranking, which in turn will attract more visitors and consequently more revenues for their owners generated as Online.io tokens. Author: SpockSenior
Title: [ANN][ICO][OIO] ONLINE - Together we can change the internet 🔴|🔴
Body: Since there was a question before about PoET I found this part in the whitepaper  "Proof-of-elapsed time (PoET) - (Reference #4) is a relatively new concept. Coins are distributed based on the proof that the user was doing some specific action for a rather long period of real time. Proof of time algorithm was invented by Intel and it is mainly associated with their hardware platform that provides very fast consensus model. It generates random numbers (wait time) on miner’s nodes and then chooses the node with the lowest number. So, it works like a lottery but with more complex algorithm designed to provide more optimizations. Intel promises that this algorithm cannot be broken by external actions and provides honest consensus model. This makes PoET perfect for private Blockchain when you need performant distributed storage and don’t want to force your hardware to make complex computations. The only minus is the restriction on Intel’s platform (Sawtooth Lake). The proof-of-elapsed time has not become popular and well adopted yet. But in the near future it may be intensively developed. Future adoptions may not be the exact algorithm designed by Intel, but rather some variations of the concept."

Author: MrSlave
Title: [ANN][ICO][OIO] ONLINE - Together we can change the internet 🔴|🔴
Body: The price, as listed in their whitepaper is 0.04 USD. It's important to note there are 3 types of coins, so keep in mind when buying:  -Online Ethereum token (OIO). OIO Tokens are the key element in the ecosystem. The web operators will be required to stake OIO Tokens in order to use our technology and mine ICE tokens. (through Proof-of-Stake and Proof-of-Online algorithms). -ICE Ethereum token (ICE). The purpose of the ICE coin is to be used for micropayments and daily use. -Trust token (TST). Exists only within the private Blockchain. It is used for stimulating users to rank websites and for ranking gamification.

In order to capitalize on their websites, the operators will also appeal to promoting ads, and hence they put their webpages and consequently their visitors to the risk of being the victims of bad ads, or other types of malware software. Solution: Online.io platform will integrate a custom anti-malware and ad-blocking solution that will be made available to end users, so they can enjoy a better experience on all websites. Author: Online.io
Title: [ANN][ICO][OIO] ONLINE - Together we can change the internet 🔴|🔴
Body: We don't have any direct competitor as our idea is Unique and also our new consensus algorithm proof-of-online which removes the traditional ads revenue for website operators and opens a new revenue stream for them.  Quote from: Dr. Van Nostrand on May 06, 2018, 07:51:16 AM Can you please explain this proof of online algorithm?I never heared for it before.I know about pos,pow,but not this.  You can find the details in our whitepaper: https://online.io/download/OIO-Whitepaper.pdf After reading our whitepaper if you still have questions i will be gladly to answer you.  Quote from: kalehon on May 07, 2018, 07:02:07 PM So what is the purpose of the tokens?  I understand you are raising money for the development of the app but what would someone use these tokens for? Quote from: Tyrannah on May 06, 2018, 04:04:48 PM Why do you need both ICE and OIO ?  OIO are the tokens sold at the Token Generation Event and generated only once. They are the fuel for our ecosystem, website operators that will integrate our solution will require staking OIO tokens in order to mine ICE tokens using the proof-of-online algorithm. OIO Token holders that are not website operators will still be able to earn ICE tokens by using the Proof-of-Stake algorithm and keeping the OIO tokens in a smart contract. A good example is NEO which is required to generate GAS. ICE tokens will be integrated into our merchant system, more details about that can be found in our whitepaper.  Quote from: WillerTex on May 06, 2018, 04:26:25 PM How many tokens you plan to sell during private sale?  If you can disclose that info of course  If all tokens will be sold at private then the Pre and Public Token Generation Event won't take place. You can buy the OIO tokens from the exchanges after the TGE is over if you didn't managed to buy.  Quote from: PlanetCrypto on May 07, 2018, 03:01:04 PM This is a challenging project, the traditional Internet search engine will have a big impact, like a BAT before the project, in fact, people in the use of BAT browser when encryption can also get some money, this is a very good promotion and selection, the OIO's prospects are very seductive. Quote from: Endimyon on May 06, 2018, 06:36:29 PM I was doing some research and from what I was able to see it seems that BAT would be the main competitor, seems to me they are doing exactly those things that OIO is trying to do.  Brave ( BAT ) it's actually a browser while our solution comes with extensions for all major browsers like Chrome, Firefox, Opera, IE and also applications for mobile. Brave shows certain ads that comply with their policy while we DON'T show any ads. Our solution also brings a new revenue stream for the website operators and earn ICE tokens without having to show their visitors any ADS so they can focus more on the quality of their content, websites.  Quote from: Cepane11ka on May 06, 2018, 07:55:06 PM When does ICO actually starts? It's private sale at the moment right?  At the moment we are doing our private sale. We are currently doing an Asian tour, more details can be found here: https://medium.com/online-io-blockchain-technologies/asian-private-investors-meetups-2018-ba5655295ed1  Quote from: BestdruidEU on May 07, 2018, 07:41:08 AM Do you have any kind of referral system going on?  We have a 5% referral program. You need to register on our website and you will get your refferal link after.  Quote from: Dr. Van Nostrand on May 07, 2018, 08:35:10 AM Can everyone join the sale,or there will be some restrictions?I know that often people from China and United States cant join.  Unfortunately, due to regulations we are not able to accept US, China for our Pre/Public ICO.  Quote from: DammeClaudeVanJean on May 07, 2018, 10:20:22 AM Will you offer VPN services as well?  We will actually offer a peer to peer VPN service with residential IPs where users will also be able to monetize their shared bandwidth.  Quote from: crownjewel on May 07, 2018, 01:54:42 PM Where do you stand on the topic of GDPR?  We are 100% GDPR compliant. You can find that in our WP also.  Quote from: Kavorka on May 07, 2018, 06:19:48 PM Where exactly is your team headquarters?  Our company is based in United Kingdom and we have our tech office in Ukraine at Zfort and also another office in Bucharest, Romania.  Quote from: Jocolyn on May 07, 2018, 07:01:46 PM Will there be an opportunity for main net testers or beta testers?  Yes, we will be doing many of our testings openly.   Best wishes  Alexandru Iulian Florea CEO & Founder Online.io Blockchain Technologies ltd

Author: Online.io
Title: [ANN][ICO][OIO] ONLINE - Together we can change the internet 🔴|🔴
Body: Basically, user's can share their network with other users and get paid when someone is using their bandwidth. Microleaves is the largest residential peer to peer proxy network in the world and we have very high volume of users and companies that are in need of residential Ips. Users will get paid for each GB that they share which will be a really good revenue. We already have the infrastructure which we have been working for the past 14 months on it and we delayed the release just to tight it to Online.io project.  Quote from: BigcountryRoy on May 07, 2018, 08:33:35 PM Can we buy OIO by sending funds directly from Binance?I can't withdraw from Binance at the moment...  You can send funds from Binance but you will need to set an ERC20 supported address to receive the OIO tokens on.  Best wishes  Alexandru Iulian Florea CEO & Founder Online.io Blockchain Technologies ltd

Author: MrSlave
Title: [ANN][ICO][OIO] ONLINE - Together we can change the internet 🔴|🔴
Body: I know a lot of people here heard about PoW and PoS, but Online is mentioning in its whitepaper something new and it's quite cool.  'Proof-of-elapsed time (PoET) is a relatively new concept. Coins are distributed based on the proof that the user was doing some specific action for a rather long period of real time. Proof of time algorithm was invented by Intel and it is mainly associated with their hardware platform that provides very fast consensus model. It generates random numbers (wait time) on miner’s nodes and then chooses the node with the lowest number.'

Author: snowcommander
Title: [ANN][ICO][OIO] ONLINE - Together we can change the internet 🔴|🔴
Body: "Our ultimate goal is to reinvent the World Wide Web experience by placing people’s privacy as our top priority, thus offering a more secure, non-trackable, without malware and ad free Internet. "  I am very interested in this part - how do you plan to achieve it?

Author: Online.io
Title: [ANN][ICO][OIO] ONLINE - Together we can change the internet 🔴|🔴
Body: Quote from: snowcommander on April 30, 2018, 07:56:56 PM "Our ultimate goal is to reinvent the World Wide Web experience by placing people’s privacy as our top priority, thus offering a more secure, non-trackable, without malware and ad-free Internet. "  I am very interested in this part - how do you plan to achieve it?  Historically, users had to pay a visible or hidden fee to browse the Internet, the most popular methods of payment currently in use are Advertising, Ecommerce and Subscription. There are no/or at least next to none/truly free sites currently operating, even Wikipedia asks for donations from its user base.  Our solution brings a new revenue stream for the website operators that integrate our solution and offer their visitors access to a website without Ads, Trackers, Malware while at the same time earn ICE tokens for their visitors based on time spent on the website. End users will be able to navigate on websites that won't show any Ads or have Trackers, Malware. There will also be Extensions for all popular browsers, mobile applications which will be free for the end users. By creating an ecosystem when ICE tokens are generated from the User's engagement to the content of the website operators, the website operators can generate profits by selling the ICE tokens and the users benefit from an ad-free, private, secure internet browsing experience. In essence, ICE tokens represent the exchange of value between user's interaction, and the content provided.  More information can be found on our website and whitepaper, check also our explainer video. https://online.io  Best wishes  Alexandru Iulian Florea CEO & Founder Online.io Blockchain Technologies ltd
